Class ForkShape

java.lang.Object
  de.weltraumschaf.jebnf.gfx.shapes.AbstractShape

All Implemented Interfaces:
Paintable, Shape
public class ForkShape
extends RectangularShape

Forks are a combination of either a "straight shape" with direction StraightShape.Directions.NORT_SOUTH or StraightShape.Directions.WEST_EAST shape and a "curve shape" with direction CurveShape.Directions#North_EAST, CurveShape.Directions#North_WEST, CurveShape.Directions.SOUTH_EAST, or CurveShape.Directions.SOUTH_WEST.

Author:
Sven Strittmatter
